{"tid":805583,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"領養兔仔，不要買！🐰🐰🌟🌟🏆🏆","createTime":"2018-09-04T02:52:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T08:37:12.000Z","uid":197098,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2fda6e8c036bb0e255d5b1b28f03b0de1a0ea4bd","tid":805583,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T02:52:31.000Z","msg":"實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>參觀然後領養</strong></span>，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=FjfXLVNGf54Mqq3HKCvM3Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ffe0776f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>領養了兔兔，改變了牠的生命！</ins></strong>🐰🌟🌟</span><br />\n<br />\n牠還會經常跳兔子舞(binky) ! <br />\n<br />\n(兔子binky是兔子最開心的狀態。當牠們binky 時，這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活。)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>以下video 可看到：</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMu27kYckovg&d=FjfXLVNGf54Mqq3HKCvM3Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=f1deb72b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg</a>"},{"pid":"ce454b89be8677e55d41ec6a5335d8f40e7672a5","tid":805583,"uid":62513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:33:13.000Z","msg":"幫你推推"},{"pid":"f40cc34e42a9f48056145469556bf5db917294c4","tid":805583,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e880d1608909119277ee34da5b1df4fa8d89727","tid":805583,"uid":40119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T06:36:41.000Z","msg":"睇到新聞想養，不過屋企已經有兩隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32aa5507622a3276b625066b164697245380c93","tid":805583,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T07:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75090fd3d64c90b3cacdbff8a3cff2e39b5ab48","tid":805583,"uid":7555,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T07:49:42.000Z","msg":"你怎麼可以吃兔兔"},{"pid":"06b110124070341f55e0334ba9af845ebbf203f0","tid":805583,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T13:03:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兔兔打籃球打到累了, 然後去了睡覺💤🐰🐰</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rQcoSxQj95s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrQcoSxQj95s&d=FjfXLVNGf54Mqq3HKCvM3Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=d05dcd2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rQcoSxQj95s</a>"},{"pid":"22ca1799f48af7bab2c48c65bb8572b16c560596","tid":805583,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T13:12:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>為什麼兔仔鼻子會移動? </ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n兔子的鼻子移動時代表當時專注，可以因為牠對某事物感興趣或好奇，移動得越快就越專注。但鼻子移動亦可以代表焦慮，要看當時的情況。通常兔子感到輕鬆時牠們鼻子會移動。<br />\n<br />\n你可以做一個有趣的實驗(或可變成一個對話技巧)：趴在地上面向兔子，重複地把上唇卷入上牙下面來模仿兔子鼻子移動(如果有鬍子會更有效)，然後改變速度看看兔子的反應。移動速度首先比兔兔慢，然後加速，牠可能會因為專注程度增加而跟你加速，然後你再減慢，此時牠亦可能跟著減慢。牠亦可能會覺得迷惑。(最好做之前告訴家人以免覺得怪）<br />\n<br />\n以下video 可看到兔子鼻子移動：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8Tozjowr2JY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8Tozjowr2JY&d=FjfXLVNGf54Mqq3HKCvM3Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a458d35b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8Tozjowr2JY</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><em>更多關於兔子鼻子移動:</em></span> <a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/follow-my-nose/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2Ffollow-my-nose%2F&d=FjfXLVNGf54Mqq3HKCvM3Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=f7e7beb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/follow-my-nose/</a>"},{"pid":"635263269997a68a634e3a129861b9a126bc629e","tid":805583,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:26:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>兔子會不會發夢？</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n當然會，以下videos 可看到：<br />\n<br />\n發夢同主人玩：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s-7b9X5x_Ro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ds-7b9X5x_Ro&d=FjfXLVNGf54Mqq3HKCvM3Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=c8d1396a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s-7b9X5x_Ro</a> <br />\n<br />\n發夢喝水：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/koTWmdwLlp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkoTWmdwLlp8&d=FjfXLVNGf54Mqq3HKCvM3Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7d778a6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/koTWmdwLlp8</a> <br />\n<br />\n發夢吃香蕉：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-nDqlfAW-xE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-nDqlfAW-xE&d=FjfXLVNGf54Mqq3HKCvM3Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a16f32f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-nDqlfAW-xE</a>"},{"pid":"07add3a741082e95fa8575e3fa40f82f7db5cf1c","tid":805583,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:22:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兔子技能表演🐰🌟🏆🏆👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fun07SfeTOI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFun07SfeTOI&d=FjfXLVNGf54Mqq3HKCvM3Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=42c90099\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fun07SfeTOI</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g_dI8437VqM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dg_dI8437VqM&d=FjfXLVNGf54Mqq3HKCvM3Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EG